				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$\approx 10^{6}$\end{document}


				 times brighter than the corona itself. In fact, the Earth’s sky is also much brighter than the corona – of the order



